    "title": "Career Opportunity Logistics Manager at Gati Consulting Pvt Ltd",
    "description": "Are you a skilled Logistics Manager looking for your next big career move? Gati Consulting Pvt Ltd in Madurai offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Gati Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nGati Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure proper handling, packaging, and labeling of goods\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in Vendor Management\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in TMS\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Madurai, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Gati Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
